                            Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s.
                        </p>
                        <a href="{{ path('page_apply_insurance', {'name': 'maxima'}) }}" class="rounded order-online">Оформить онлайн</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row margin-bottom-50 border-bottom-40-red">
                    <div class="col d-flex align-items-center flex-column justify-content-center">
                        <p class="text-justify">
                            Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.
                            Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s.
                        </p>

                        <a href="{{ path('page_apply_insurance', {'name': 'unica'}) }}" class="rounded order-online">Оформить онлайн</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3">
                        <img src="{{ asset('assets/page/img/unica-logo.jpg') }}" alt="UNICA pojišťovna" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row margin-bottom-50 border-bottom-40-red">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img src="{{ asset('assets/page/img/ergo-logo.png') }}" alt="ERGO pojišťovna" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col d-flex align-items-center flex-column justify-content-center">
