                        </p>

                        <a href="{{ path('page_apply_insurance', {'name': 'pvzp'}) }}" class="rounded order-online">Оформить онлайн</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3">
                        <img src="{{ asset('assets/page/img/pvzp-logo.png') }}" alt="PVZP pojišťovna" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <section id="contactUs" class="pt-5 pb-5 background-red">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center text-white font-weight-bold mb-4 pt-3">Получите больше информации по телефону</h2>
            <p class="text-center text-white mb-3">
